<h3>Thesaurus</h3>

<p>In thesaurus mode, enter a word for which you need to find an alternate word with a
 similar meaning and click the <b>Search</b> button.</p>

<p>If any words are found in the online thesaurus, a list of words will be displayed.  Clicking
 on a word will display all of the definitions of the word.</p>
 
<p><b>NOTE:</b> Some words in the online thesaurus do not have definitions in the online
 dictionary.</p>